@GlujDrive.Server_HostAddress = http://localhost:5199

GET {{GlujDrive.Server_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###
### Semantic-search status (host only)
GET {{GlujDrive.Server_HostAddress}}/api/ai/status
Accept: application/json

### Queue the bundled/downloaded AI installation (host only)
POST {{GlujDrive.Server_HostAddress}}/api/ai/install

### Hybrid filename and semantic search
POST {{GlujDrive.Server_HostAddress}}/api/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "sunset at the beach",
  "pageSize": 60
}
